  "And, by the way, that’s no different to any other industry.’",
  "",
  "This is, of course, true and it gives food companies two choices.",
  "They can premiumise and sell the same number of units for more money, or they can sell more units to more people more often.",
  "In the corporate arms race for money, every company is doing all these things simultaneously as fast as they can.",
  "",
